import React from 'react'; import '../../assets/style/FlightRecord.css'; import Departure from '../../assets/images/departures.png'; import Arrival from '../../assets/style/arrivals.png'; const FlightRecord = ({ location, destination, departure, airline, duration, arrival, price, travelType }) => { return (

{location}

-

{destination}

Departure

{departure.time}

Airport: {departure.airport}

Airline

{airline}

Duration

{duration}

Arrival

{arrival.time}

Airport: {arrival.airport}

Price: {price}

{travelType}

); }; export default FlightRecord;
